<h3 id="content">Content</h3>

<p><strong>Preliminary Course content:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Week 1: Dynamic closed position</li>
  <li>Week 2: Back to Swing out</li>
  <li>Week 3: Over-rotation</li>
  <li>Week 4: New leading points</li>
  <li>Week 5: Jazz up</li>
  <li>Week 6: Instructorsâ€™ favourite</li>
  <li>Week 7: Studentsâ€™ choice</li>
  <li>Week 8: Competition skills</li>
